snippet.title: Sword Bros - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Sword Bros is freeform swordfighting at breakneck speeds.
Sword Bros is reptilian reflexes.
Sword Bros is machiavellian strategy.
Sword Bros is double jump dash cancel to swinging parry wavedash to reverse spin back-throw counter-slash.
Sword Bros is fun with swords.

A game by Drew Wallace (Jamestown+) 
Music by Francisco Cerda (Jamestown+, Gunpoint, Subterfuge)
Art by Mike Ambrogi Primo (Jamestown+) 

Releasing November 10th on Steam and Itch.io
http://store.steampowered.com/app/680990/Sword_Bros/
http://drewwallace.itch.io/swordbros
http://www.swordbrosgame.com
